title: effect to Section 7 of Chapter 3 of Title I of Part IV of Regulation (EU) 2016/429
heading: 1. These are the Import and Export of Animals and Animal Products
text_raw:
1. These are the Import and Export of Animals and Animal Products 
(Animal Health Certificates) Regulations 2021 (Amendment) Regulations 2022.

title: effect to Section 7 of Chapter 3 of Title I of Part IV of Regulation (EU) 2016/429
heading: 2. The Import and Export of Animals and Animal Products (Animal Health
text_raw:
2. The Import and Export of Animals and Animal Products (Animal Health 
Certificates) Regulations 2021 are amended, in Regulation 5 (2) (b), by inserting 
“caprine animal, “after “camelid animal,”.
